@page "/"

<PageTitle>AI Chat</PageTitle>

<div class="home-page">

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow">
            <span class="hero-badge">
                <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l2 2"/></svg>
                Powered by Azure OpenAI
            </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Your AI workspace,<br /><span class="hero-accent">built for real work.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
            Chat with multiple models, upload documents for grounded answers, and keep your conversation history
            secure with Azure-backed identity and encryption.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
            <a class="cta-primary" href="/chat">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 2L11 13"/><path d="M22 2L15 22L11 13L2 9L22 2Z"/></svg>
                Start chatting
            </a>
            <a class="cta-secondary" href="/chat">New conversation</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">3</span>
            <span class="stat-label">AI models available</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">∞</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Conversation history</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">File types supported</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">🔒</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Azure Key Vault encryption</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Multi-model chat</h3>
            <p>Switch between GPT-5.4, DeepSeek V4 Pro, and Grok 4.3 mid-conversation. Each response is tagged with the model that produced it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Document grounding</h3>
            <p>Upload PDFs, Word docs, CSVs, images, and more. The assistant draws on your content to give precise, context-aware answers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Enterprise security</h3>
            <p>Microsoft Entra ID authentication, SQL-backed storage with field-level encryption, and keys managed by Azure Key Vault.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><polyline points="1 4 1 10 7 10"/><path d="M3.51 15a9 9 0 101.85-4.6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Regenerate &amp; iterate</h3>
            <p>Not happy with a response? Regenerate it instantly using the same or a different model without losing your conversation.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-banner">
        <div class="cta-banner-inner">
            <div class="cta-banner-text">
                <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
                <p>Open a chat window and ask anything.</p>
            </div>
            <a class="cta-primary" href="/chat">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 2L11 13"/><path d="M22 2L15 22L11 13L2 9L22 2Z"/></svg>
                Open chat
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="home-footer">
        Developed by <strong>Bori Olaleye</strong> &copy; 2026
    </footer>

</div>
